        <updateDate>2021-04-29T20:29:43Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><STRONG></STRONG><b><b>Providing Accountability Through Transparency Act of 2021</b></b></p> <p>This bill requires the notice of a proposed rule by a federal agency to include the internet address of a summary of the rule. The summary must be 100 words or fewer, written in plain language, and posted on regulations.gov.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
